                <head>63. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>At a meeting of the <gloss target="#t_ANZUS1">ANZUS</gloss> Council, held in
                    Washington, September 24, Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DJF1"
                        >Dulles</persName> commented on United States policy concerning the Taiwan
                    Strait; a record of the meeting is scheduled for publication in the compilation
                    on United States policies with respect to the East Asian-Pacific area in a
                    forthcoming volume.</p>
            </div>
